@NODE 5 "Reservoir Dogz - Help."
                                @{FG HIGHLIGHT}5. BUGS/CAVEATS@{FG TEXT}
                                
  There are not a lot of bugs in this game, but one important one which
  does allow you to cheat is that the coppers don't shoot back while you
  are reloading. If you cannot work out how to cheat from this info, then
  you're THICK! (But you lose points every time you reload!)

  If you experience a bug which causes a copper to suddenly shift position
  to a place where he shouldn't, send me a letter and I will stamp out the
  problem. This was a severe problem on levels 4 and 5, but I managed to
  iron them out. I haven't had any more since, but If you experience one,
  let me know so I can sort it aht! 
  
  There are cheats for unlimited ammo, invulnerability, and level skips to
  each of the levels (excluding level 1). There is also a 'cheat' which
  disables the other cheats. All I'm saying is that you enter them on the
  high score table.
  
  If you find other bugs, send a report to the address given on the
  contact information page.
  
